17namespace webrtc {
18
19// TODO(bugs.webrtc.org/12000): Note that this extensions is being developed and
20// the wire format will likely change.
21class RtpVideoLayersAllocationExtension {
22 public:
23 using value_type = VideoLayersAllocation;
24 static constexpr RTPExtensionType kId = kRtpExtensionVideoLayersAllocation;
25 static constexpr const char kUri[] =
26 "http://www.webrtc.org/experiments/rtp-hdrext/video-layers-allocation00";
27 static bool Parse(rtc::ArrayView<const uint8_t> data,
28 VideoLayersAllocation* allocation);
29 static size_t ValueSize(const VideoLayersAllocation& allocation);
30 static bool Write(rtc::ArrayView<uint8_t> data,
31 const VideoLayersAllocation& allocation);
32};
33
34} // namespace webrtc
